The paper discusses the formal semantics of the P4 programming language for programmable packet processors, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and network architecture and protocols (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of formal analysis tools for P4 programs, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper mentions the detection of unportable code, which could fall under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO).
